text: Gonnoscodina (Gonnoscodìna) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Oristano in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 477 people lived there. Its area is 8.82 km². It is 112 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Oristano
title: Gonnoscodina
